	<h2 style="margin: 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 112, 192); min-height: 32px; border-bottom-width: 2px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 112, 192); text-align: justify;"><span class="autonum" data-original-title="" placeholder="1" style="font-weight: 500; line-height: 20px; border-radius: 80% 100% 90% 20%; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: block; float: left; margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; max-width: 100%; padding: 4px 10px; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(0, 112, 192);" title="">☆</span><span style="font-size:18px;"><span style="line-height: 22.3906px;">牙龈发炎肿痛的原因是多种多样的，一般来说有如下几种：</span></span></h2>
</section>
